%% Diagram: Cutover Readiness Gates
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    start([Cutover checklist])
    g1{Lag under SLO?}
    g2{Reconciliation clean?}
    g3{Shadow reads OK?}
    g4{Rollback rehearsed?}
    g5{Flags + on-call ready?}
    go[Bounded cutover]
    watch{Healthy?}
    done([Stabilize then decommission])
    fail["Any NO → remediate + restart<br/>throttle · fix pipeline · fix semantics<br/>rehearse rollback · assign commander"]

    start --> g1 -->|yes| g2 -->|yes| g3 -->|yes| g4 -->|yes| g5 -->|yes| go --> watch
    watch -->|yes| done
    watch -->|no| fail
    g5 -->|no| fail
